  schema:name "The Expert System Pattern: Knowledge Base and Inference Engine" ;
  schema:description "Expert systems decompose into a knowledge base (structured facts) and an inference engine (closure operations). This separation maps precisely to the fiber algebra plus nucleus pattern in algebraic logic." ;
